txt.en: 'Hey, you! I hear you sneakin' about!'
'Well... I am hardly surprised that you stand here before me. These grave-robbers are weak and soft - they lack the resolve that my benefactors seek.'
'They believe they were chosen by the Eye to serve. Such fools... they are merely a tool of my people.'
'These men you aid are beyond helping. They would sooner fight amongst themselves than against a foe.'
'My people will engulf this land in terror and when at last the dark shadow of our master falls upon this realm, both Rohan and Gondor shall fall!'
'Neither you, the impotent fools upon the field, or these pitiful Gondorians will stand in our way!'
'An empty victory... your doom rises in the East....'
